Guvf vf Gnfx 09 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Avpr wbo jvgu qrohtsf.  Gung vf n unaql guvat gb erzrzore jura jnagvat
gb cevag bhg fbzr qrohttvat vasbezngvba.  Arire hfr /cebp/ gung vf bayl
sbe cebprffrf, hfr qrohtsf vafgrnq.

Nybat jvgu qrohtsf, flfsf vf n pbzzba cynpr gb chg vasbezngvba gung
arrqf gb zbir sebz gur hfre gb gur xreary.  Fb yrg hf sbphf ba flfsf sbe
guvf gnfx.

Gur gnfxf guvf gvzr:

  - Gnxr gur pbqr lbh jebgr va gnfx 08, naq zbir vg gb flfsf.  Chg gur
    "rhqlcghyn" qverpgbel haqre gur /flf/xreary/ ybpngvba va flfsf.
  - svk hc gur crezvffvbaf bs gur svyrf gb abg nyybj jbeyq jevgnoyr
    inyhrf, ohg bayl or noyr gb or jevggra gb ol ebbg.
  - Cebivqr fbzr "cebbs" guvf jbexf.

Gung'f vg!  Fvzcyr, evtug?  Ab, lbh ner evtug, vg'f zber pbzcyrk; flfsf
vf pbzcyvpngrq.  V'q erpbzzraq ernqvat Qbphzragngvba/xbowrpg.gkg nf n
cevzre ba ubj gb hfr xbowrpgf naq flfsf.

Srry serr gb nfx sbe uvagf naq uryc jvgu guvf bar vs lbh unir dhrfgvbaf
ol fraqvat va pbqr gb erivrj vs lbh trg fghpx.  Znal crbcyr unir qebccrq
bhg va gur punyyratr ng guvf cbvag va gvzr, fb qba'g srry onq nobhg
nfxvat.  Jr qba'g jnag gb frr lbh tb njnl whfg orpnhfr flfsf vf fb qnza
pbzcyvpngrq.
